io.oasp.gastronomy.restaurant.staffmanagement.service.api.rest

Interface StaffmanagementRestService

  • All Superinterfaces:
    RestService
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StaffmanagementRestServiceImpl

    @Path(value="/staffmanagement/v1/staff")
@Consumes(value="application/json")
@Produces(value="application/json")
public interface StaffmanagementRestService
extends RestService
    The service class for REST calls in order to execute the methods in Staffmanagement.
